<h1>About Clinic Management System</h1>
<hr />

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      The Clinic Management System is designed to streamline the operations of healthcare clinics by providing an
      integrated solution for managing products,
      online purchases, and generating comprehensive reports. Our goal is to help clinics enhance efficiency, reduce
      administrative overhead,
      and improve patient care through better inventory management and data-driven insights.
    </p>

    <h2>Core Features</h2>
    <div class="card-deck">
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">User Management</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Secure user accounts with role-based access control, authentication, and profile
            management.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Product Management</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Comprehensive inventory management system with product categorization, search
            functionality, and stock tracking.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-deck">
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Online Purchase</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Streamlined ordering process with shopping cart functionality, order tracking, and
            payment integration.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Reporting</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Data visualization and insights through customizable reports on sales, inventory, and
            customer activity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Technology</h2>
    <p>
      Built with modern technologies including ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, and SQL Server,
      our system follows clean architecture principles for maintainability and scalability.
    </p>
  </div>

